public class BreakIteratorSentenceSplitter
extends AbstractSentenceSplitter
implements SentenceSplitter

Splits text into sentences using regular expressions.

Uses a Java BreakIterator to identify candidate sentences. Several heuristics are used to correct the initial sentence identification.
